referralReceived.body:
TO: Dr. {{referringPhysician}}
FROM: Mount Sinai Fertility Referrals
DATE: {{currentDate}}
RE: {{patientName}} (DOB: {{patientDOB}})

Dear Dr. {{referringPhysician}},

Thank you for your referral of the above-named patient to Mount Sinai Fertility.

We have received the referral and are currently processing it. The patient will be contacted by one of our MD administrative coordinators to schedule an appointment.

If you have any questions or require additional information, please contact us at 416-586-4800 ext. 2778.

Sincerely,
{{signature}}

